original: Edgren, Folke Georg Vilhelm, civilingenjör, vicekonsul, Kalmar, f. 23/10/ 10 i Kalmar av konsul A. E. o. Kristina Lundqvist. G. 36 m. Britta Sandgren. Barn: Göran f. 43. — Civiling:-ex. v. CTH (kemi o. kem. teknol.). Driftsing. v. A-B Kalmar chokladfabr. 36-41, fabr.-chef o. dir. sed. 41. Po-kns vicekonsul fr. 44.
translated: Edgren, Folke Georg Vilhelm, engineer, vice-consul, Kalmar, b. 23/10/1910 in Kalmar to consul A. E. and Kristina Lundqvist. Married in 1936 to Britta Sandgren. Children: Göran b. 1943. Graduated as an engineer from Chalmers University of Technology (chemistry and chemical technology). Worked as an operating engineer at A-B Kalmar chocolate factory from 1936-1941, then became factory manager and director from 1941 onwards. Appointed as vice-consul in 1944.
